  ('medical-tech-moex-04518', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '結核桿菌中，抗生素與其抗藥性基因的配對，下列何者最不適當？', '["rifampin：rpoB", "isoniazid：katG", "ethambutol：embB", "streptomycin：penA"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4264efaaa5ed", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d1fc110b5521", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111100", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、111年專技...", "original_question_number": 67, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
